TopicTitle: Parts Missing in VAB on Mac

Articles.Content:
For several mods, (Roverdude's Exploration Pack, Stockalike Station Parts Expansion, Karbonite, etc.) parts will not show up in the VAB. The ones that do work perfectly. As far as I can tell, whether a part will show up is random.

Modlist:

BahaD's Constellation Pack

Docking Alignment Indicator

FireCrew

Kerbal Alarm Clock

Kerbal Attachment System

Kerbal Engineer Redux

ModStatistics

Porkjet's Habitats

SurfaceLights

Tweakscale

Kommit Nucleonics

Thanks!
